description:
In this karaoke video, we'll be singing our favorite songs from when we all get to heaven!
Whether you're a believer or not, this is a fun and upbeat karaoke video that you don't want to miss! We'll be singing all our favorite songs, accompanied by the lyrics so you can really belt out the tunes!

Title: When We All Get to Heaven
Author: E. E. Hewitt (1898)
Performed and mixed by C Lalhmuaka, 3 Sisters youtube production.
